#### 改变秘钥可导出属性

要找到秘钥创建的地方，就要熟悉创建秘钥的api

`generateKey`

_algorithm_

一个对象，用于定义要生成的算法类型，并提供所需的参数。

_extractable_

一个布尔值，表示生成的密钥是否可被 [`SubtleCrypto.exportKey()`](https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/SubtleCrypto/exportKey) 和 [`SubtleCrypto.wrapKey()` (en-US)](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/SubtleCrypto/wrapKey) 方法导出。

_keyUsages_

示例

~~~js
let key = await window.crypto.subtle.generateKey(
  {
    name: "AES-GCM",
    length: 256
  },
  true,
  ["encrypt", "decrypt"]
);
~~~

#### 导出秘钥

使用indexedDB的js api，导出数据库的秘钥

~~~js
function indexDbget(session,key) {
    return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {
        const transaction = db.transaction(session, 'readwrite');
        const store = transaction.objectStore(session);

        const request = store.get(key);
        request.onsuccess = function (e) {
            console.log('get imgFiles success');
            console.log(e.target.result);
            resolve(e.target.result);
        };

        request.onerror = function (e) {
            console.error('get imgFiles fail');
            reject(e);
        };
    });
}

//打开数据库，返回一个数据库请求
openRequest  = window.indexedDB.open("netflix.player");
 
openRequest.onupgradeneeded = function(e) {
    console.log("Upgrading...");
}

//若打开成功则触发此请求
openRequest.onsuccess = function(e) {
    console.log("Success!");
    db = e.target.result; //获取数据库对象
    console.log(db)
    promise = indexDbget('namedatapairs','mslstore');  //获取目标数据的promise
    promise.then(values => {
        
    console.log(values.data.encryptionKey);
        
    })
}

openRequest.onerror = function(e) {
    console.log("Error");
    console.dir(e);
}

~~~

在chrome的devtools的代码段执行上面这段脚本可以获取秘钥的对象

下面就是要导出秘钥为base64形式

~~~js
function indexDbget(session,key) {
    return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {
        const transaction = db.transaction(session, 'readwrite');
        const store = transaction.objectStore(session);

        const request = store.get(key);
        request.onsuccess = function (e) {
            console.log('get imgFiles success');
            console.log(e.target.result);
            resolve(e.target.result);
        };

        request.onerror = function (e) {
            console.error('get imgFiles fail');
            reject(e);
        };
    });
}



//打开数据库，返回一个数据库请求
openRequest  = window.indexedDB.open("netflix.player");
 
openRequest.onupgradeneeded = function(e) {
    console.log("Upgrading...");
}

//若打开成功则触发此请求
openRequest.onsuccess = function(e) {
    console.log("Success!");
    db = e.target.result; //获取数据库对象
    console.log(db)
    promise = indexDbget('namedatapairs','mslstore');  //获取目标数据的promise
    promise.then(values => {
        
        key = values.data.encryptionKey;
         exported =  window.crypto.subtle.exportKey("raw", key);
        exported.then(exp => {

            const exportedKeyBuffer = new Uint8Array(exp);
            const base64String = window.btoa(String.fromCharCode(...exportedKeyBuffer));
            console.log("AES-CBC秘钥: "+base64String);
        });
   
    });
}

openRequest.onerror = function(e) {
    console.log("Error");
    console.dir(e);
}

~~~

上面是完整的代码，会将AES-CBC秘钥的值打印在控制台里

~~~js

 function stringToByte(str) {
    var bytes = new Array();
    var len, c;
    len = str.length;
    for(var i = 0; i < len; i++) {
        c = str.charCodeAt(i);
        if(c >= 0x010000 && c <= 0x10FFFF) {
            bytes.push(((c >> 18) & 0x07) | 0xF0);
            bytes.push(((c >> 12) & 0x3F) | 0x80);
            bytes.push(((c >> 6) & 0x3F) | 0x80);
            bytes.push((c & 0x3F) | 0x80);
        } else if(c >= 0x000800 && c <= 0x00FFFF) {
            bytes.push(((c >> 12) & 0x0F) | 0xE0);
            bytes.push(((c >> 6) & 0x3F) | 0x80);
            bytes.push((c & 0x3F) | 0x80);
        } else if(c >= 0x000080 && c <= 0x0007FF) {
            bytes.push(((c >> 6) & 0x1F) | 0xC0);
            bytes.push((c & 0x3F) | 0x80);
        } else {
            bytes.push(c & 0xFF);
        }
    }
    return bytes;


}
~~~
